---
title: Falafel and Hot Honey Veggie 'Nduja Mayo Wraps with Greek Style Salad Cheese, Baby Gem Salad and Chips
description: Inspired by some of the world's most popular street food, these tasty Falafel and Hot Honey Veggie 'Nduja Mayo Wraps are perfect for a casual sharing-style vegetarian dinner.
